{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-weifeng-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-weifeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-weifeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·衛風·003.1", "text_original": "碩人其頎，衣錦褧衣，齊侯之子，衛侯之妻，東宮之妹，邢侯之姨，譚公維私。", "text_normalized": "碩人其頎，衣錦褧衣，齊侯之子，衛侯之妻，東宮之妹，邢侯之姨，譚公維私。", "notes": "碩人 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-weifeng-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-weifeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-weifeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·衛風·003.2", "text_original": "手如柔荑，膚如凝脂，領如蝤蠐，齒如瓠犀，螓首蛾眉，巧笑倩兮，美目盻兮。", "text_normalized": "手如柔荑，膚如凝脂，領如蝤蠐，齒如瓠犀，螓首蛾眉，巧笑倩兮，美目盻兮。", "notes": "碩人 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-weifeng-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-weifeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-weifeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·衛風·003.3", "text_original": "碩人敖敖，說于農郊，四牡有驕，朱幩鑣鑣，翟茀以朝，大夫夙退，無使君勞。", "text_normalized": "碩人敖敖，說于農郊，四牡有驕，朱幩鑣鑣，翟茀以朝，大夫夙退，無使君勞。", "notes": "碩人 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-weifeng-003__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-weifeng-003", "source_id": "guofeng-weifeng-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·衛風·003.4", "text_original": "河水洋洋，北流活活，施罛濊濊，鱣鮪發發，葭菼揭揭，庶姜孽孽，庶士有朅。", "text_normalized": "河水洋洋，北流活活，施罛濊濊，鱣鮪發發，葭菼揭揭，庶姜孽孽，庶士有朅。", "notes": "碩人 Chinese stanza 4."}
